About Me

I’m a versatile software engineer who enjoys tackling challenging problems. My experience spans building AI‑powered pipelines, developing full‑stack web applications, and designing automation workflows. Whether extracting insights from marketing videos, orchestrating research assistants, or creating dynamic booking systems, I strive to deliver polished, user‑centric products.

Projects

Flight Search Web Application

A full‑stack flight search and booking system built with Python, Flask and MySQL.

  • Intuitive search by city, airport code or dates, with options for one‑way or return trips.
  • Customer portal to manage bookings, pay for tickets and leave ratings & reviews.
  • Staff dashboard to create flights, adjust schedules, view passengers and generate reports.
GitHub Repo
Campaign Video Analysis Pipeline

Automates scraping and analysis of award‑winning marketing campaigns from video platforms.

  • Scrapes and normalises video URLs from sources like YouTube and Vimeo.
  • Uses Google’s AI to analyse video content and extract relevant insights.
  • Employs a two‑phase architecture—cloud and local—for scalable processing.
GitHub Repo
Research Assistant Agent

Intelligent agent to summarise and retrieve research documents using LangChain/LangGraph.

  • Combines dense embeddings and keyword matching for hybrid document retrieval.
  • Orchestrates multi‑step tasks with LangGraph for accurate summarisation.
  • Includes a small dataset and Streamlit interface for interactive Q&A.
GitHub Repo
Social Media Image Builder

Generates photorealistic social images by combining generative AI models and user preferences.

  • Collects user mood, style and creative prompts through an agentic flow.
  • Automatically extracts elements and searches for reference images using internet search.
  • Composes the final image using Gemini models on a Node.js backend.
GitHub Repo
RoboCafe

Robotics project to automate café tasks using an XArm robot.

  • Implements control scripts for an XArm robotic arm to pick, place and serve items.
  • Includes calibration routines and dataset generation tools for training.
  • Designed to demonstrate automation in a café environment.
GitHub Repo
